                <Header>Climate Change</Header>
                <Paragraph>Together with other natural and anthropogenic health stressors, climate change affects human health and disease in many ways. It intensifies some existing health threats and causes the emergence of new ones. Not everyone is equally at risk: Age, economic resources, location, and other factors influence outcomes.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
